{"lemma":"ذَرِّيَّةٍ","slug":"ذَرِّيَّةٍ","root":"ذ.ر.ر","root_slug":"ذ-ر-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ذ-ر-ر","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"ذَرِّيَّةٍ","root":"ذرر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":32},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n13739","n13749","n13849","n13847"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B0%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%91%D9%8A%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"alternative form of ذَرَا (ḏarā)","tags":["alt-of","alternative"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to disperse, to scatter","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to carry away (dust) (of the wind)","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to winnow (grain)","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to atomize","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of ذُرْوَة (ḏurwa, “peak, summit”)","tags":["form-of","plural","transitive"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n13739","headword_ar":"ذُرِّيَّةٌ","root":"*r","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) the most chaste form, (Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ir~iy~apN","text_ar":"ذِرِّيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ariy~apN","text_ar":"ذَرِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", this last without a sheddeh to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"r","text_ar":"ر"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) [respecting the derivation of which see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*rA^","text_ar":"ذرا"},{"kind":"text","text":",] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Children,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"offspring,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, Msb, K,) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ar~N","text_ar":"ذَرٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) of a man, (S, K,) [and of genii: see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*rA^","text_ar":"ذرا"},{"kind":"text","text":",] male or female: (IAth:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"little ones,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"young ones."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb.) ―         -b2-  Also (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Progenitors, or ancestors."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, MF.) ―         -b3-  Also (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Women."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, K.) ―         -b4-  Used in a sing. as well as a pl. sense. (Mgh, Msb, K.) ―         -b5-  Pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ur~iy~aAtN","text_ar":"ذُرِّيَّاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and (sometimes, Msb)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*araAriY~u","text_ar":"ذَرَارِىُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb, K.) [In the CK, the latter pl., with the article, is written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al*~araAriY","text_ar":"الذَّرَارِى"},{"kind":"text","text":", without a sheddeh to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b6-  For examples, see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*rA^","text_ar":"ذرا"},{"kind":"text","text":".]"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","Mgh","IAth"]},{"entry_id":"n13749","headword_ar":"ذُرِّيَّةٌ","root":"*rA^","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, Mgh, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ir~iy~apN","text_ar":"ذِرِّيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ar~iy~apN","text_ar":"ذَرِّيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) [or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ariy~apN","text_ar":"ذَرِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", without a sheddeh to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"r","text_ar":"ر"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to the Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*r","text_ar":"ذر"},{"kind":"text","text":",] always pronounced by the Arabs without"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) accord. to some, (TA,) from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al*~aro'u","text_ar":"الذَّرْءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, TA;) so says Th; (M;) the measure of the first being"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuE~uwlapN","text_ar":"فُعُّولَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuE~iylapN","text_ar":"فُعِّيلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [so that it is originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ur~uw'apN","text_ar":"ذُرُّوءَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ur~iyoy^apN","text_ar":"ذُرِّيْيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";] (TA;) but the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"'","text_ar":"ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"is suppressed because of frequency of usage: (M:) accord. to others, from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al*~ar~u","text_ar":"الذَّرُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifying “ the act of scattering; ” because God scattered the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*r~y~p","text_ar":"ذرّيّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"upon the earth; and the measure is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuEoliy~apN","text_ar":"فُعْلِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fuE~uwlapN","text_ar":"فُعُّولَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [if the latter,] the word being originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ur~uwrapN","text_ar":"ذُرُّورَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the last"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"r","text_ar":"ر"},{"kind":"text","text":"being changed into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":", in a manner similar to the case of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqaD~ati AlEuqaAbi","text_ar":"تَقَضَّتِ العُقَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in which"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqaD~aDat","text_ar":"تَقَضَّضَت"},{"kind":"text","text":"becomes"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqaD~ayat","text_ar":"تَقَضَّيَت"},{"kind":"text","text":"and then"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taqaD~at","text_ar":"تَقَضَّت"},{"kind":"text","text":"; so that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ur~uwrapN","text_ar":"ذُرُّورَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"becomes"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ur~uwyapN","text_ar":"ذُرُّويَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and then"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ur~iy~apN","text_ar":"ذُرِّيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Children,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"offspring,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, Mgh, K,) of a man, and used as a sing. also, (Mgh,) or of men and of jinn, or genii: (S, K:) pl. ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ur~iy~aAtN","text_ar":"ذُرِّيَّاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*r","text_ar":"ذر"},{"kind":"text","text":") and sometimes]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*araAriY~u","text_ar":"ذَرَارِىُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"habo liY mino ladunoka","text_ar":"هَبْ لِى مِنْ لَدُنْكَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ur~iy~apF Tay~ibapF","text_ar":"ذُرِّيَّةً طَيِّبَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the Kur iii. 33, meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Give me, from Thee, a good offspring"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Mgh.) And in a trad. of Ibn-'Omar,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fajaEalaniY fiY Al*~ur~iy~api","text_ar":"فَجَعَلَنِى فِى الذُّرِّيَّةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And he put me among the little ones,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"young ones."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) ―         -b2-  It is also applied to signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Progenitors:"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the saying, in the Kur [xxxvi. 41],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamalonaA *ur~iy~atahumo fiY A@lofuloki Alma$oHuwni","text_ar":"حَمَلْنَا ذُرِّيَّتَهُمْ فِى ا@لْفُلْكِ المَشْحُونِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We carried their progenitors in the laden ark"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (T.) ―         -b3-  And it is used also to signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Women;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[because they are the sources of offspring;] (T, Mgh, TA;) like as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"samaA='N","text_ar":"سَمَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is used to signify “ rain: ” (TA:) as in the saying of 'Omar,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Huj~uwA biAl*~ur~iy~api","text_ar":"حُجُّوا بِالذُّرِّيَّةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Perform ye the pilgrimage with the women"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (T, Mgh, TA. [See his saying in full, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riboqN","text_ar":"رِبْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".])"}],"source_refs":["T","S","M","Mgh","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n13849","headword_ar":"ذُرِّيَّةٌ","root":"*rw and *rY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*arowN","text_ar":"ذَرْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n13847","headword_ar":"ذَرِيَّةٌ","root":"*rw and *rY","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A she-camel by means of which one conceals himself from the objects of the chase:"},{"kind":"text","text":"on the authority of Th: but the more approved word is with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"d","text_ar":"د"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dariy~apN","text_ar":"دَرِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or, accord. to AZ,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dariyoy^apN","text_ar":"دَرِيْيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (M.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}